it%20became%20an%20institution%2C%20but%20not%2C%20technically%2C%20a%20restaurant%2C%20as%20local%20regulations%20prohibited%20it.%20Instead%2C%20the%20Duryeas%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bpicnic%20shack%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7af3f4d2-5e51-4079-b223-81dd66702b3c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Perry%20Duryea%20III%20sold%20the%20business%20to%20billionaire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-rowan-apollo-ceo-succession-question-kleinman-zelter-kvalheim-belardi-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Rowan%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20reported%20%246.3%20million.%20Over%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20gone%20are%20the%20picnic%20tables%20and%20relatively%20low%20prices%2C%20and%20in%20their%20place%20are%20more%20upscale%20booths%2C%20a%20refurbished%20dock%2C%20and%20%24300%20seafood%20towers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20Monday%20in%20August%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20check%20out%20what%20Duryea's%20is%20like%20now%2C%20almost%2010%20years%20after%20its%20rebranding%20under%20Rowan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20my%20visit%20was%20like%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20I%20got%20for%20%24230.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDuryea's%20is%20a%20Montauk%20institution.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22deck%20at%20duryea's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a75dc8a17a8c5b40534066%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuryea's%20began%20as%20a%20fish%20market%20in%20the%20'20s.%20It%20became%20%3Cem%3Esome%20%3C%2Fem%3Eversion%20of%20the%20restaurant%20that%20is%20known%20and%20loved%20today%20in%201948%2C%20when%20Perry%20Duryea%20Jr.%20(the%20former%20owner%20Chip%20Duryea's%20father)%20returned%20home%20from%20World%20War%20II%2C%20per%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhalebonemag.com%2Fthe-beginning-of-the-end-chip-duryea%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhalebone%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it's%20expanded%20from%20a%20plain%20fish%20market%20to%20two%20restaurants%20(one%20in%20Montauk%2C%20another%20in%20Orient%20Point)%2C%20rentable%20cottages%2C%20and%20two%20beach%20clubs%20(Orient%20Point%20and%20the%20Riviera%20Maya%20in%20Mexico).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDuryea's%20doesn't%20take%20reservations.%20I%20arrived%20shortly%20after%20it%20opened%20at%20noon%20on%20a%20Monday%2C%20and%20there%20was%20already%20a%20line.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryea's%20line%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a75f88cfc04e97619bcb54%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%2C%20naively%2C%20thought%20that%20on%20a%20Monday%20in%20August%2C%20Duryea's%20wouldn't%20be%20crowded.%20I%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20waited%20around%2030%20minutes%20to%20be%20seated%20on%20the%20deck.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lobster%20deck%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a75fc2cfc04e97619bcb5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20true%20indoor%20seating%2C%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20high-tops%20with%20no%20chairs.%20The%20deck%20is%20the%20place%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHere's%20how%20crowded%20it%20was%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20after%20opening.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryea's%20dock%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a75ffbcfc04e97619bcb64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20see%20a%20boat%20parked%20at%20the%20dock%20%E2%80%94%20at%20many%20restaurants%20on%20the%20eastern%20end%20of%20Long%20Island%2C%20you%20can%20pull%20right%20up%20to%20Duryea's%20and%20hop%20off%20your%20boat%20for%20some%20fresh%20lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20tables%20and%20seating%20were%20light%20wood%20and%20white%2C%20making%20it%20the%20perfect%20summer%20photo%20op.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22seating%20at%20duryea's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a5f39da17a8c5b40532a46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20believe%20me%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Elot%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20photos%20were%20being%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20restaurant%20has%20learned%20to%20poke%20fun%20at%20its%20reputation.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryea's%20famous%20sign%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a76077a17a8c5b405340d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20sign%20proclaimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20all%20famous%20here.%26quot%3B%20I%20bet%20some%20people%20would%20disagree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20Duryea's%2C%20you%20order%20by%20marking%20your%20choices%20on%20the%20menu%20and%20taking%20it%20to%20the%20counter.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryea's%20ordering%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a8b4faa17a8c5b40535756%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20all%20part%20of%20the%20idea%20that%20this%20was%20once%20a%20casual%20place%20to%20hang%20out%20by%20the%20ocean%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20come%20a%20long%20way%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20menu%20is%20certainly%20not%20cheap.%20Most%20of%20those%20items%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20shared%20between%20two%20to%20three%20people%2C%20but%20still%2C%20it's%20pricey.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryea's%20menu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a77a45194a2d49b8aef65b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeafood%20generally%20isn't%20known%20as%20a%20cheap%20cuisine%2C%20but%20here%2C%20seafood%20towers%20cost%20up%20to%20%24345%2C%20lobster%20rolls%20are%20%2445%2C%20and%20a%202-pound%20lobster%20costs%20%2494.%20Even%20more%20classic%20dishes%20can%20ring%20up%20the%20bill%3A%20A%20grilled%20cheese%20is%20%2421%2C%20the%20house%20salad%20is%20%2439%2C%20and%20a%20roasted%20chicken%20is%20%2483.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ordered%20the%20lobster%20Cobb%20salad%20(%2497)%2C%20a%20lobster%20roll%2C%20and%20a%20single%20basket%20of%20fries%20(%2416)%2C%20and%20three%20Diet%20Cokes%20(%246%20each).%20We%20also%20got%20three%20cups%20of%20water%2C%20which%20were%20%242%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20window%20was%20lively.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222143%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryea's%20employees%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a77b64194a2d49b8aef67b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221607%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWas%20I%20a%20%3Cem%3Elittle%20%3C%2Fem%3Esurprised%20that%2C%20with%20such%20high%20prices%2C%20you%20had%20to%20go%20up%20and%20place%20your%20order%20yourself%3F%20Sure%2C%20but%20it%20gave%20me%20an%20excuse%20to%20walk%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20almost%20as%20if%20Duryea's%20is%20trying%20to%20have%20it%20both%20ways%20by%20keeping%20the%20casual%20beachy%20vibes%20of%20the%20original%20store%20with%20a%20food%20window%20and%20bringing%20the%20elevated%20vibes%20of%20the%20Hamptons%20with%20its%20aesthetic%20and%20high%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20walking%20around%2C%20I%20explored%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20store.%20Duryea's%20merch%20was%20for%20sale.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryeas%20merch%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a77ba4194a2d49b8aef684%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20small%20market%20and%20a%20boutique%20attached%20to%20the%20main%20Duryea's%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20also%20got%20a%20good%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20seafood%20that%20would%20be%20consumed%20soon.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryea's%20lobster%20and%20clams%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a8b514cfc04e97619be240%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spotted%20lobsters%2C%20oysters%2C%20and%20clams%20in%20this%20cooler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20came%20back%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20dig%20in.%20Here's%20the%20lobster%20Cobb%20salad.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22salad%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a5faddcfc04e97619bb5ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20give%20it%20to%20them%3A%20This%20was%20huge.%20It%20easily%20fed%20two%20people%2C%20and%20probably%20could've%20fed%20at%20least%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20contained%20lettuce%2C%20tomatoes%2C%20avocado%2C%20hard-boiled%20eggs%2C%20bacon%20bits%2C%20a%20creamy%20tarragon%20dressing%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20giant%20hunks%20of%20lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThey%20did%20not%20skimp%20on%20the%20lobster.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221606%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lobster%20at%20duryea's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a77c9b194a2d49b8aef6cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221204%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20didn't%20throw%20in%20tiny%20chunks%20of%20lobster%20%E2%80%94%20the%20pieces%20were%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20my%20palm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20was%20it%20really%20worth%20%2497%3F%20I'd%20say%20no.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lobster%20salad%20duryea's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a8b43b194a2d49b8af094b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20got%20past%20the%20top%20layer%20of%20lobster%20meat%2C%20this%20was%20essentially%20a%20huge%20bowl%20filled%20with%20lettuce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20love%20the%20dressing%20either%20%E2%80%94%20I%20found%20it%20to%20be%20a%20bit%20too%20tangy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20recommend%20sticking%20with%20the%20lobster%20roll%2C%20an%20old%20favorite.%20You%20also%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20lobster%2C%20but%20it's%20roughly%20half%20the%20price.%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20homemade%20chips%2C%20which%20were%20delicious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20fries%20rocked%2C%20though.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221682%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fries%20at%20duryea's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a8b690a17a8c5b405357be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221345%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fries%20were%20the%20perfect%20amount%20of%20crispy%2C%20and%20I%20prefer%20shoestring-style%20fries%20to%20almost%20any%20other.%20And%2C%20with%20just%20three%20people%2C%20a%20single%20basket%20was%20the%20perfect%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20clear%20that%2C%20more%20than%20anything%2C%20you're%20paying%20for%20the%20ambiance%20at%20Duryea's.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryeas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a77e5ca17a8c5b40534507%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJonah%20Rosenberg%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20perfect%20day%20to%20be%20sitting%20on%20the%20bay%2C%20drinking%20an%20ice-cold%20Diet%20Coke%2C%20and%20snacking%20on%20some%20lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20on%20a%20budget%2C%20I%20would%20probably%20recommend%20skipping%20Duryea's%2C%20or%20at%20least%20keeping%20your%20order%20small.%20After%20the%20tip%2C%20our%20lunch%20for%20three%20people%20came%20out%20to%20%24230.68.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuryea's%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20about%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBut%20if%20you%20have%20the%20means%2C%20Duryea's%20should%20be%20on%20your%20Montauk%20itinerary.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22duryea's%20dock%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a