nted%20to%20start%2C%20and%20looked%20down%20at%20the%20range%20meter%20and%20realized%20we%20were%20not%20going%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20next%20charger%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Parker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParker%20and%20Kraus%20briefly%20considered%20using%20a%20tiny%201800-watt%20gas%20generator%20to%20charge%20the%20Tesla%2C%20one%20mile%20at%20a%20time%2C%20before%20ditching%20the%20trailer%20at%20an%20exit%20ramp%20and%20%26quot%3Bcrawling%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-diner-grand-opening-hollywood-review-weird-fun-good-food-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enearest%20supercharger%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20experienced%20it%20many%20times%20since.%20It%20is%20a%20nightmare%20to%20go%20trailering%20with%20an%20EV%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Parker%2C%20who%20described%20the%20initial%20road%20trip%20as%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Lightship's%20inception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKraus%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20Tesla's%20finance%20team%20for%20five%20years%20in%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20towing%20problem%20was%20the%20%26quot%3BAchilles'%20heel%26quot%3B%20of%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20products%20now%20that%20have%20300%2C%20350-mile%20range%2C%20which%20is%20awesome%2C%20but%20guess%20what%3F%20If%20you%20use%20them%20to%20tow%2C%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20your%20range%20drops%20by%20two-thirds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed384b71-eb33-455d-ad97-1384a26260ab%5C%22%3ETariff%20turmoil%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELightship%2C%20which%20has%20raised%20over%20%2460%20million%20since%20it%20was%20founded%20in%202020%2C%20now%20employs%20around%20100%20people%20at%20its%20Colorado%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20limited%20edition%20%24250%2C000%20AE.1%20%26quot%3BCosmo%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20company%20is%20working%20on%20more%20affordable%20versions%20of%20its%20motorized%20electric%20RV%2