%20to%20present%2C%20how%20to%20work%20in%20a%20team%2C%20how%20to%20write%20emails%20to%20CEOs%20of%20companies.%20You%20learn%20how%20to%20be%20in%20Zoom%20meetings%20with%20them%20and%20not%20mess%20up.%20You%20learn%20about%20different%20industries%3B%20I%20worked%20for%20so%20many%20different%20and%20interesting%20clients.%20It's%20a%20business%20school%20MBA%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20camaraderie%20is%20also%20insane.%20You%20have%20young%2C%20ambitious%20people%20from%20everywhere%20on%20your%20team%2C%20and%20you're%20working%20hard%2C%20then%20you're%20partying%20hard%2C%20and%20it's%20like%20you're%20not%20sleeping%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20it's%20up%20and%20out%20%E2%80%94%20you%20either%20make%20the%20next%20step%20or%20you%20leave.%20I%20wasn't%20motivated%20anymore%20after%20two%20years%2C%20because%20you're%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20PowerPoint%20and%20Excel%2C%20and%20it%20was%20just%20not%20intellectually%20stimulating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20bored%20with%20it%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20and%20found%20an%20AI%20voice%20agent%20startup%20called%20Leaping%20AI.%20We%20got%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyc-founders-younger-under-more-pressure-beacause-ai-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EY%20Combinator%3C%2Fa%3E's%20winter%20cohort%20this%20year%20and%20then%20raised%20%244.7%20million%20in%20seed%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20consulting%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20able%20to%20understand%20business%20and%20economy.%20I%20know%20what%20a%20P%26amp%3BL%20is%20and%20I%20understand%20that%20businesses%20have%20to%20make%20money%20and%20they%20have%20costs%20and%20what%20exactly%20does%20that%20mean.%20I%20understand%20how%20to%20conduct%20myself%20when%20I'm%20talking%20to%20CEOs%20that%20I%20want%20to%20sell%20my%20product%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20very%20confident.%20I%20learned%20that%20in%20consulting.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBefore%20consulting%2C%20I%20was%20this%20random%20computer%20science%20grad%20with%20no%20people%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-career-progression-soft-skills-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleadership%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20even%20though%20we're%20still%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20I'm%20confident%20enough%20to%20lead%20teams%20and%20be%20the%20guy%20at%20the%20helm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a5d25d1-f954-48db-84c2-1be23975fce8%5C%22%3EConsulting%20doesn't%20fully%20prepare%20you%20for%20entrepreneurship%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20some%20of%20the%20highest-achieving%20individuals%20in%20the%20world%20in%20consulting%2C%20but%20it%20is%20very%20hard%20out%20of%20consulting%20to%20do%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20in%20consulting%2C%20you%20don't%20meet%20any%20tech%20people.%20You%20only%20meet%20other%20business%20people%2C%20which%20can%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20found%20a%20startup%2C%20since%20most%20of%20them%20today%20are%20in%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsulting%20is%20also%20a%20risk-averse%20culture.%20Entrepreneurship%20is%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20hitting%20rock%20bottom.%20You%20don't%20have%20a%20job%2C%20nobody%20pays%20you%2C%20and%20nobody%20knows%20who%20you%20are.%20There's%20a%20high%20risk%20that%20it%20may%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-projects-deloitte-kpmg-ey-pwc-consulting-accountacy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsulting%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20client%20will%20tell%20you%20what%20the%20goal%20is%20and%20what%20they%20need.%20The%20path%20is%20already%20given.%20Whereas%20in%20entrepreneurship%2C%20there%20is%20no%20path.%20You%20have%20to%20forge%20your%20own%20and%20decide%20what%20you're%20going%20to%20do%20and%20then%20do%20it%20even%20when%20there's%20high%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20consulting%2C%20whatever%20you%20do%2C%20you%20have%20to%20align%20i