4-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20for%20%26quot%3Bdata%20collection%20operators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20roles%20have%20involved%20performing%20and%20recording%20basic%20household%20tasks.%20The%20job%20postings%20said%20the%20operators%20would%20be%20required%20to%20wear%20motion%20capture%20suits%20and%20virtual%20reality%20headsets%20for%20extended%20periods%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20until%20late%20June%2C%20the%20project%20involved%20teleoperating%20Optimus%20and%20training%20the%20robot%20via%20the%20motion%20capture%20suits.%20Workers%20spent%20time%20troubleshooting%20issues%20with%20the%20suit%20and%20with%20Optimus%2C%20which%20limited%20the%20amount%20of%20data%20the%20team%20was%20able%20to%20collect%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20training%20shift%2C%20workers%20have%20focused%20on%20recording%20their%20own%20movements%20using%20a%20set%20of%20five%20cameras%20made%20in-house%2C%20insiders%20said.%20The%20cameras%20are%20attached%20to%20a%20helmet%20and%20a%20heavy%20backpack%20worn%20by%20the%20worker.%20The%20cameras%20point%20in%20all%20directions%2C%20giving%20the%20AI%20model%20data%20that%20orients%20it%20precisely%20in%20its%20environment%2C%20the%20insiders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristian%20Hubicki%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20robotics%20lab%20for%20FAMU-FSU's%20engineering%20school%2C%20said%20the%20various%20camera%20angles%20likely%20allow%20Tesla%20to%20collect%20more%20minute%20details%2C%20%26quot%3Blike%20the%20location%20of%20joints%20and%20fingers%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20properly%20place%20the%20robot%20in%20space.%20The%20videos%20could%20also%20be%20a%20way%20of%20augmenting%20the%20previous%20data%20they%20collected%20using%20teleoperation%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20receive%20specific%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20perform%20the%20tasks%20for%20training%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hand%20movement%20and%20ensuring%20the%20movements%20look%20as%20human%20as%20possible.%20They%20can%20spend%20months%20performing%20the%20same%20simple%20task%2C%20one%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Aitken%2C%20a%20robotics%20expert%20with%20the%20University%20of%20Sheffield%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Tesla%20will%20likely%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20teach%20Optimus%20using%20actions%20that%20could%20apply%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorking%20at%20this%20scale%2C%20they%20must%20have%20a%20generalized%20set%20of%20actions%20or%20else%20it%20would%20take%20forever%20to%20do%20all%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Aitken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Tesla%20could%20employ%20a%20similar%20strategy%20to%20Physical%20Intelligence%2C%20a%20company%20that%20feeds%20robots%20vast%20amounts%20of%20demonstration%20data%20so%20they%20can%20learn%20transferable%20skills%20and%20apply%20them%20flexibly%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20memorizing%20how%20to%20perform%20a%20single%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e214a32-e132-40b4-8cb9-e780884e3661%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20very%20Tesla%20way%20of%20doing%20robotics'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20strategy%20is%20in%20line%20with%20Tesla's%20training%20process%20for%20its%20self-driving%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20autonomous%20vehicle%20companies%20use%20LiDAR%20and%20radar%20sensors%20to%20teach%20their%20software%2C%20Tesla%20primarily%20relies%20on%20a%20collection%20of%20cameras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20uses%20data%20collected%20from%20millions%20of%20Tesla%20owners%2C%20whose%20vehicles%20are%20equipped%20with%20between%20eight%20and%20nine%20cameras.%20Musk%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1894444545301205133%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tesla%20released%20its%20driver-assist%20software%20in%20China%20after%20training%20its%20AI%20system%20with%20publicly%20available%20videos%20of%20streets%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20acknowledged%20during%20an%20earnings%20call%20in%20January%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20training%20needs%20for%20Optimus%20humanoid%20robot%2C%20are%20probably%20at%20least%20ultimately%2010x%20of%20what%20is%20needed%20for%20the%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20Tesla%20way%20of%20doing%20robotics.%20No%20one%20else%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20this%20at%20the%20same%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20Aitken%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey'll%20need%20as%20much%20data%20as%20they've%20used%20to%20train%20their%20cars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlan%20Fern%2C%20an%20AI%20and%20robotics%20expert%20at%20Oregon%20State%20University%2C%20said%20training%20Optimus%20will%20be%20an%20even%20more%20daunting%20project%20for%20Tesla%20than%20developing%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDriving%20is%20just%20one%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Learning%20primarily%20from%20videos%20%26quot%3Bwould%20require%20the%20robot%20to%20understand%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20video%2C%20and%20then%20have%20the%20skills%20to%20accomplish%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20things%20it%20can%20learn%20by%20watching%20and%20others%20it%20will%20need%20to%20physically%20practice%2C%20whether%20in%20a%20simulator%20or%20the%20real%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Tesla%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agkay%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Egkay%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20248-894-6012.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%2