rch%20and%20development%20closely.%20For%20Synthesia%2C%20it's%20a%20case%20of%20letting%20AI%20talent%20know%20that%20its%20products%20can%20get%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20customers%2C%20which%20includes%2070%25%20of%20Fortune%20500%20companies%2C%20%26quot%3Bvery%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20That%20can%20help%20attract%20and%20retain%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20who%20want%20to%20see%20AI%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20consumers%20across%20the%20stack%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20like%20Synthesia%20should%20also%20prioritize%20career%20growth%20to%20help%20retain%20talent%2C%20Florez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20ensure%20we've%20identified%20our%20talent%20and%20had%20transparent%20conversations%20about%20career%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20noticed%20certain%20topics%20around%20personal%20development%20and%20career%20growth%20have%20really%20mattered.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20how%20any%20great%20startup%20should%20get%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f845e14d-0b55-4866-8bf2-1e45db2c225e%5C%22%3EMind%20the%20compensation%20gap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20also%20need%20to%20look%20inward%20at%20their%20compensation%20spread%2C%20said%20Kim%20Scott%2C%20a%20former%20tech%20employee%20who%20has%20coached%20CEOs%20and%20published%20books%20on%20workplace%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20Apple%20and%20Google%2C%20said%20the%20disparities%20in%20salaries%20in%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20have%20become%20a%20bigger%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20your%20VPs%20are%20being%20paid%20100%20times%20more%20than%20your%20entry-level%20employees%2C%20you've%20got%20a%20real%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20companies%20need%20to%20calibrate%20compensation%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20gap%20isn't%20too%20big%20and%20doesn't%20cause%20tensions%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quo