20to%20invest%20in%20a%20deal%2C%20how%20to%20underwrite%20it%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-real-estate-syndications-can-help-investors-earn-passive-income-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20syndication%20works.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Syndication%20is%20where%20a%20group%20of%20investors%20pools%20their%20capital%20to%20invest%20in%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20hanging%20out%20in%20those%20circles%20of%20local%20investors%2C%20learning%20and%20making%20investments.%20I%20met%20a%20lot%20of%20like-minded%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20invest%20passively%20while%20managing%20full-time%20jobs.%20My%20first%20investment%2C%20with%20some%20of%20those%20friends%2C%20was%20in%20an%20operating%20business%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20doing%20this%20alongside%20working.%20In%20the%20early%20mornings%2C%20I%20reviewed%20investment%20decks%2C%20private%20placement%20memoranda%2C%20and%20sponsorship%20documents.%20In%20the%20evenings%2C%20I%20met%20with%20peers%20to%20discuss%20investment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20schedule%3B%20sometimes%20it%20was%20super%20late%20or%20super%20early%2C%20and%20you%20would%20react%20whenever%20the%20deals%20came%20in.%20I%20was%20killing%20myself%20working%20a%20full-time%20job%20and%20doing%20as%20much%20as%20I%20was%20doing%20on%20my%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22876686a7-9afb-4606-bd13-3baf1bbe068f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere's%20no%20work-life%20balance%2C%20but%20I'm%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20layoff%20came%2C%20it%20was%20a%20major%20dent%20in%20my%20pocket.%20The%20steady%20paycheck%20was%20gone.%20But%20by%20then%2C%20I%20had%20some%20investments%20bringing%20in%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20considered%20applying%20for%20other%20roles%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20but%20l%20decided%20that%20I%20no%20longer%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20W-2%20employee%2C%20and%20I%20would%20focus%20on%20my%20ventures%20ins