ng%20there%2C%20and%20tells%20me%20she%20first%20learned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fproperty-tax-by-state%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproperty%20taxes%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20studying%20for%20her%20license.%20But%20she%20soon%20started%20posting%20listings%20to%20Facebook%2C%20something%20none%20of%20her%20coworkers%20were%20doing%2C%20and%20made%20her%20first%20sale.%20Not%20long%20after%2C%20the%20older%20agents%20were%20coming%20to%20her%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20use%20social%20media%20for%20their%20listings.%20%26quot%3BI%20really%20was%20able%20to%20capture%20like%20a%20whole%20new%20set%20of%20first-time%20homebuyers%2C%26quot%3B%20Harvey%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20early%20career%20years%20did%20set%20her%20apart%20from%20her%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20still%20in%20college.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20mind%20boggling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20making%20at%20that%20point%20%2480%2C000%2C%20they%20had%20accrued%20%2480%2C000%20in%20debt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20it's%20still%20something%20of%20a%20rarity%20to%20see%20a%20baby-faced%20real%20estate%20agent%20or%20teenager%20selling%20life%20insurance%2C%20the%20young%20people%20in%20licensure%20jobs%20I%20spoke%20to%20say%20that%20succeeding%20means%20not%20just%20learning%20the%20trade%20but%20competing%20against%20ageist%20stereotypes.%20The%20median%20age%20of%20a%20first-time%20home%20buyer%20has%20risen%20to%20an%20all-time-high%20of%2038%2C%20according%20to%20NAR.%20That's%20up%20from%20an%20average%20age%20of%2033%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-listings-zillow-america-europe-france-italy-house-hunting-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZillow%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20idea%20of%20having%20a%20newly%20minted%2C%2018-year-old%20real%20estate%20agent%20guide%20you%20through%20the%20biggest%20financi