amp_articleshow%2F123498102.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Harvard%20professor%20on%20why%20AI%20'evangelism'%20is%20harming%20students'%20career%20prospects%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Student%20on%20Harvard%20campus%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a759decfc04e97619bca8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlex%20Green%2C%20a%20Harvard%20professor%2C%20explains%20his%20concerns%20with%20AI%20use%20in%20classrooms.%3Cp%3EZiyu%20Julian%20Zhu%2FXinhua%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDebate%20is%20rampant%20over%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20incorporate%20AI%20in%20classrooms.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlex%20Green%2C%20a%20Harvard%20professor%2C%20said%20he's%20concerned%20that%20AI%20use%20is%20damaging%20students'%20communication%20skills.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20that%20while%20there's%20a%20place%20for%20AI%2C%20intensive%20teacher%20training%20to%20understand%20its%20risks%20is%20vital.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20a%20student%20who%20spent%20an%20entire%20semester%20researching%20and%20writing%20a%2020-page%20paper.%20You've%20poured%20time%20and%20effort%20into%20the%20assignment%2C%20and%20you're%20looking%20forward%20to%20hearing%20your%20professor's%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20you%20get%20a%20mediocre%20grade%20and%20three%20short%20paragraphs%20of%20vague%20comments%2C%20and%20you%20wonder%3A%20Did%20ChatGPT%20grade%20my%20essay%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%2C%20it%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20scenario%20a%20student%20recounted%20to%20Alex%20Green%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.blpress.org%2Fbooks%2Fa-perfect-turmoil%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthor%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20professor%20at%20Harvard's%20Kennedy%20School.%20Green%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BAI%20evangelism%26quot%3B%20push%20%E2%80%94%20efforts%20to%20use%20AI%20across%20classrooms%20to%20make%20both%20teaching%20and%20learning%20easier%20%E2%80%94%20is%20doing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%2C%20undermining%20critical%20relationships%20between%20teachers%20and%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20teachers%20or%20students%20are%20using%20AI%2C%20Green%20said%20it's%20leading%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20%26quot%3Bso%20many%20fundamental%20communication%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20knowledge%20and%20reasoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%2C%20who%20teaches%20policy%20communications%20and%20op-ed%20writing%2C%20said%20AI%20could%20also%20harm%20his%20students'%20career%20prospects%20if%20they're%20pursuing%20fields%20like%20communications%20and%20rely%20on%20AI%20to%20build%20those%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20job%2C%20in%20part%2C%20is%20to%20help%20prepare%20them%20to%20go%20get%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20heard%20from%20some%20of%20his%20students%20that%20their%20prospective%20employers%20required%20them%20to%20share%20their%20screens%20while%20they%20take%20writing%20tests%20to%20ensure%20they're%20not%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20what%20would%20I%20be%20doing%20for%20them%20if%20I%20said%20to%20them%2C%20'No%2C%20no%2C%20you%20can%20just%20use%20these%20indiscriminately%2C%20and%20how%20you%20write%20and%20how%20you%20think%20and%20how%20you%20synthesize%20ideas%20doesn't%20really%20matter%3F'%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20you%20a%20parent%2C%20educator%2C%20or%20student%20with%20thoughts%20to%20share%20on%20AI%20usage%20in%20the%20classroom%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20tech%20leaders%20and%20educators%20have%20been%20pushing%20initiatives%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummit-learning-school-curriculum-funded-by-zuckerberg-faces-backlash-brooklyn-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincorporate%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20classrooms.%20While%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2Fanalytics%2F659819%2Fk-12-teacher-research.aspx%3Fthank-you-report-form%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurveys%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20shown%20that%20AI%20use%20has%20helped%20teachers%20save%20time%20and%20provide%20higher-quality%20lessons%2C%20there's%20minimal%20evidence%20that%20using%20AI%20to%20learn%20is%20effective.%20Additionally%2C%20AI%20is%20already%20starting%20to%20impact%20young%20people's%20job%20prospects%2C%20with%20some%20tech%20leaders%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-says-generative-ai-expect-job-cuts-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20will%20decrease%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-collar-workers-slow-job-growth-hiring-wages-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhite-collar%20job%20openings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%20said%20he's%20not%20against%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20he%20has%20used%20it%20himself%20for%20his%20work%2C%20and%20he%20allows%20it%20in%20his%20classroom%2C%20to%20an%20extent.%20But%20it's%20not%20a%20replacement%20for%20teachers%2C%20and%20heavily%20relying%20on%20it%20is%20a%20waste%20of%20a%20school's%20resources%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20here%20now%2C%20and%20you're%20in%20a%20class%2C%20and%20you%20have%20someone%20who%20is%20a%20total%20nerd%20for%20this%20and%20has%20devoted%20their%20life%20to%20every%20aspect%20of%20this.%20And%20you%20have%20me%20fully%20at%20every%20moment%20of%20every%20hour%20for%20the%20next%20eight%20weeks%20and%20beyond%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20on%20earth%20would%20you%20take%20all%20of%20that%20sacrifice%20and%20all%20of%20that%20dedication%20and%20give%20that%20over%20to%20a%20machine%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9996749-d552-4aa9-bc88-2c47a0fe0a46%5C%22%3E'The%20bible%20salesman%20version%20of%20AI'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20shortage%20of%20efforts%20to%20incorporate%20AI%20in%20education.%20Take%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkhan-academy-ceo-ai-classroom-teacher-aid-not-replacement-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKhan%20Academy%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20online%20tutoring%20organization%20established%20in%202008%2C%20which%20gradually%20started%20using%20AI%20to%20create%20lessons%20that%20personalized%20students'%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhan%20Academy%20continues%20to%20enroll%20students%2C%20but%20other%20efforts%20have%20failed.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faltschool-why-parents-leaving-2017-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAltSchool%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20backed%20by%20tech%20billionaires%20including%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20began%20to%20shutter%20four%20years%20after%20opening%20in%202013%2C%20as%20parents%20saw%20that%20their%20kids%20weren't%20excelling%20using%20technology-based%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%20said%20the%20problem%20is%20that%20many%20of%20these%20initiatives%20are%20focused%20on%20making%20learning%20as%20easy%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20that%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20people%20have%20reframed%20the%20idea%20of%20learning%20as%20something%20where%20any%20struggle%20to%20wrestle%20with%20a%20concept%20or%20think%20really%20hard%20about%20something%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20education%20is%20bad%2C%20and%20that%20what%20we%20need%20is%20for%20things%20to%20be%20as%20seamless%20and%20easy%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20there%20isn't%20a%20place%20for%20AI.%20Green%20said%20that%20he%20used%20a%20large%20language%20model%2C%20or%20LLM%2C%20to%20comb%20through%20materials%20for%20his%20research%20and%20found%20it%20helpful.%20In%20his%20classroom%2C%20he%20said%20that%20after%20five%20weeks%20of%20%26quot%3Bintensive%20non-technological%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20starts%20incorporating%20AI%20to%20help%20his%20students%20prepare%20for%20the%20political%20communications%20landscape%2C%20which%20includes%20dealing%20with%20chatbots%20and%20identifying%20falsely%20generated%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20colleges%20are%20putting%20AI%20at%20the%20forefront.%20In%20February%2C%20California%20State%20University%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.calstate.edu%2Fcsu-system%2Fnews%2FPages%2FCSU-AI-Powered-Initiative.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20initiative%20to%20become%20the%20%26quot%3Bnation's%20first%20and%20largest%20AI-empowered%20university%20system%26quot%3B%20through%20public-private%20partnerships%20to%20train%20students%20and%20teachers%20on%20AI%20technology%2C%20including%20offering%20all%20students%20and%20faculty%20access%20to%20a%20version%20of%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20federal%20level%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20is%20establishing%20a%20task%20force%20to%20promote%20AI%20in%20K-12%20classrooms%20and%20look%20into%20redirecting%20funds%20toward%20AI%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20critics%20have%20warned%20that%20the%20US%20should%20tread%20carefully.%20South%20Korea%20recently%20rolled%20back%20its%20initiative%20to%20place%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-in-school-south-korea-textbook-rollback-jobs-education-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20textbooks%20in%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20backlash%20from%20parents%20and%20teachers%20over%20a%20lack%20of%20preparation%20on%20how%20to%20best%20use%20the%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreen%20said%20that%20if%20colleges%20want%20to%20adopt%20AI%20in%20classrooms%2C%20they%20should%20mandate%20intensive%20training%20for%20faculty%20to%20understa