%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20stadium%20that%20felt%20like%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inauguration%20in%202023%2C%20Manpreet%20has%20visited%20the%20stadium%20multiple%20times%2C%20attending%20nearly%20every%20major%20league%20and%20international%20match.%20But%20during%20the%20recent%20Hockey%20India%20League%202025%2C%20something%20felt%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CExperiencing%20a%20fully%20accessible%20stadium%20was%20honestly%20a%20breath%20of%20fresh%20air%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20moment%20I%20entered%2C%20I%20could%20tell%20this%20was%20a%20space%20designed%20with%20intention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20once%2C%20Manpreet%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20help%20navigating%20narrow%20entrances%20or%20shifting%20seating.%20He%20could%20simply%20enjoy%20the%20match%20like%20every%20other%20fan%2C%20thanks%20to%20marked%20entry%20and%20exit%20points%2C%20thoughtfully%20planned%20pathways%2C%20and%20dedicated%2C%20front-row%20accessible%20seating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENicolas%20Poncelet%2C%20a%20hockey%20player%20from%20Belgium%20who%20plays%20for%20the%20Soorma%20hockey%20club%2C%20agrees%20with%20Manpreet.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20everything%20is%20well%20done%20at%20this%20hockey%20stadium.%20Several%20access%20points%20are%20without%20stairs%2C%20and%20every%20stair%20access%20is%20arranged%20specially%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Nicholas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F312600%2Fhow-can-india-be-more-disabled-friendly-inclusive-planning-in-public-events%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20made%20the%20biggest%20impact%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20the%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20the%20freedom%20it%20gave%20me.%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20thinking%20about%20getting%20from%20point%20A%20to%20B%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20just%20living%20in%20the%20mome